des:
Immerse yourself in a tranquil oasis with the Green Noise skill. Perfect for relaxation, focus, or restful sleep, this skill plays a soothing selection of nature-inspired sounds. Whether you want to unwind after a long day, find calm during meditation, or create a serene atmosphere at home, Green Noise has the perfect sound for you.

Just say "Alexa, open Green Noise" to start relaxing with the sounds of nature. 

Make every moment an experience of pure relaxation with Green Noise.
